        Features
    </Paragraph>
    <List Margin="25,0,0,0">
        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph>Color Palette Support.</Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph>Ability to enable and disable the color palette.</Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
            </List>
