        Interactions
    </Paragraph>
    <List Margin="25,0,0,0">
        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph>Enable the color palette by selecting the <Bold> Enable ColorPalette </Bold> check box.</Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph>
              Select the color palette from the <Bold> ColorPalette </Bold> combo box. Five different palettes are available with different sets of colors. When selecting a palette, the fill, border, and border thickness of the shape will change.
